OL,3,CHuw Edwards to be sentenced for making
OL,4,Cindecent images of children
OL,6,FFormer BBC news presenter Huw Edwards
OL,7,Fis due to be sentenced later today
OL,8,Fafter he admitted to having indecent
OL,9,Fimages of children.
OL,11,FIt comes as the veteran broadcaster
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to three charges of
OL,13,Fmaking indecent photographs after he
OL,14,Fwas sent 41 illegal images by
OL,15,Fconvicted paedophile Alex Williams
OL,16,Fover WhatsApp, with seven of the 41
OL,17,Fimages being of the most serious type.
OL,19,FHe will appear at Westminster
OL,20,FMagistrates Court on Monday morning.
