OL,6,FEdwards has been stripped of several
OL,7,Fhonours since his previous court
OL,8,Fappearance in August.
OL,10,FNational Eisteddfod revealed he had
OL,11,Fbeen expelled from the Gorsedd, one of
OL,12,Fthe highest honours in Welsh public
OL,13,Flife.
