OL,6,FA statement from the National
OL,7,FEisteddfod issued on Thursday, 8
OL,8,FAugust said: "Following a unanimous
OL,9,Fvote at today's Eisteddfod Court
OL,10,Fmeeting, the board of trustees has
OL,11,Fdecided to activate Section 4 of the
OL,12,Fits constitution to terminate Huw
OL,13,FEdwards' membership of the Eisteddfod
OL,14,Fand as a result, he will also be
OL,15,Fexpelled from Gorsedd Cymru."
