OL,6,FA Cardiff University spokesman
OL,7,Fconfirmed to the PA news agency that
OL,8,FEdwards resigned from both his
OL,9,Fhonorary professor title in the school
OL,10,Fof journalism, media and culture, and
OL,11,Fhonorary fellowship.
OL,13,FHis honorary fellowship of the Royal
OL,14,FWelsh College Of Music And Drama has
OL,15,Falso been withdrawn following a
OL,16,Funanimous vote by the college's board
OL,17,Fof trustees, a spokesperson for the
OL,18,Fcollege said.
