OL,6,FA mural of Edwards has been removed
OL,7,Ffrom his home village just outside
OL,8,FLlanelli.
OL,10,FThe portrait, which was part of a
OL,11,Flarger mural, was on the underpass in
OL,12,Fthe village of Llangennech, where
OL,13,FEdwards grew up.
OL,15,FIt was first unveiled in 2023 after
OL,16,Ftaking a year to paint by artist Steve
OL,17,FJenkins.
