OL,6,FHowever, Mr Jenkins has confirmed that
OL,7,Fthe portrait of Edwards has been
OL,8,Fremoved in the wake of his offences,
OL,9,Fsaying it was the "right thing to do".
OL,11,FPressure has also mounted on Edwards
OL,12,Fto return his BBC salary, which would
OL,13,Fhave seen him earn an estimated
OL,14,F#200,000 between his arrest in
OL,15,FNovember and his resignation five
OL,16,Fmonths later.
OL,18,FUK Government Culture Minister, Lisa
OL,19,FNandy told Sky News at the time: "I
OL,20,Fthink he ought to return his salary.
